[[Here is a new game I have been working on for awhile.  It's similar to
Walter Bright's Empire, but has lots more features and runs on color or
monochrome X systems.  It's kind of large, but has proved very popular at
Utah over the past three months, so much so that we've already gotten
warnings about playing too much! Please let me you if you run into any
troubles, especially with the fonts;  it's not something that X supports
too well, and I've been groping around for the right way to distribute them.
(The recently posted font editor was quite helpful!)

						stan shebs
						shebs@cs.utah.edu]]

